            <p>Over the years, he's worked every position possible at a dealership. His experience has taught him first-hand how to educate, lead, and inspire the Service Advisors and work crew in a fixed-operations department. He's perfected the process of improving customer satisfaction to an art. His proven skills have given him a well-deserved reputation for taking dozens of stores to new levels of profitability. Shaw's clients report unsurpassed sales, higher profits, and greater customer longevity.</p>
